    <h3 class="mx-auto text-center w-full my-4">One of the best practices to ensure the calmness of mind is meditation and Yoga</h3>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 bg-yellow-300 text-black py-4">Gauge stress and engagement continually</h1>
